			<article class="main">
				
					<p class="image"><img src="/~/media/Images/GatesNotes/Thinking/Tackling TB Through Innovation/20110324_Thinking-Tackling-TB-Through-Innovation_Resource_700x323.jpg" alt="Bill Gates speaks with doctors in front of the GeneXpert diagnostic system at LRS Institute of Tuberculosis and Respiratory Diseases"/></p>
					
				
				

